data.description: Come See this Beautiful Home Located in Corona De Tucson, Vail! Spacious Lot with OWNED SOLAR. The current homeowners have not had an electricity bill in years!!! This Large 4 Bedroom, 2 bath + Den + Separate Dining Room + Over Sized Laundry room + 3 Car Garage (with a tankless Hot Water Heater) and has zero carpet. The Great Room features a spacious entertainment area, a dining area and a kitchen with Granite Countertops, Large Island, Gas Range, Double Ovens and Coffee Bar! Bring your Ideas to Complete the Outdoor space on this oversized lot, one of the largest within this Community! The solar has ample of energy for pool or hot tub. This community is walkable distance to Schools, Restaurants and Hiking Trails!
